      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver for someone looking for a reliable ride at a more affordable price point. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs well, though the transmission shows some minor hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows typical wear for its age, including a small tear in the driver's seat. All major systems like the heater and brakes are functional, but the driver-side power window is slow to operate. It\u2019s a dependable car that has been maintained regularly but will eventually need some minor cosmetic and mechanical attention.",
