    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, powered by the high-string S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, sending power to the rear wheels through a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a top-end refresh to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains accessible and reliable. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by upgraded polyurethane bushings and a precise alignment, offering the communicative feedback expected of this analog icon. While the finish displays minor road-earned patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for a weekend canyon carver or a dedicated enthusiast project.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
