    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a driver who values both performance and presentation. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor road wear expected from a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is intact, and all electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, it has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service history available for your review. It starts eagerly, shifts smoothly through all gears, and handles with the precision you would expect from a vehicle of this caliber. Whether you are commuting daily or taking a long-distance weekend trip, this car offers a dependable and stylish experience that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 33800.0,
