    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the mechanical engagement is unparalleled. The chassis remains composed thanks to proactive subframe reinforcement and a recently serviced VANOS system, ensuring variable valve timing remains precise. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and ventilated rotors, it offers exceptional turn-in and stopping power. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response. A visceral, analog experience for the serious purist.",
